Comment: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:11.11,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:11119,11119}Intro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:19052,20386}Rumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.35,0:00:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:23352,26352}Senpai? Were you here\Nthe entire night?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:27119,29786}So it appears.\NWe've slept together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:33686,36152}I'm sorry.\NI'll go back to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:36152,38819}Your family may misunderstand\Nif they see us together like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.81,0:00:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:38819,42119}I don't care about what\Nanyone thinks, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.11,0:00:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:42119,44719}What I care about is you, Ruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.01,0:00:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:45019,46619}S… Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:48552,51686}Wait! I'm sick, remember?\NJust like Rumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:51886,53786}So what if you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:53786,58086}Even if I do get infected, just because you gain\Ncontrol over me, I won't become your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:00:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:58086,59719}But Senpai, that doesn't mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.71,0:01:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:59719,61052}You can call me Katsuyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.05,0:01:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:61052,65286}Waiting forever is not my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:80019,82252}What's the matter?\NDo you feel sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.55,0:01:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:82552,83852}It… It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:83852,87219}Oh, no! Did I kiss too deep?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:87219,89019}Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:89652,91486}You're awful, Katsuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.81,0:01:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:91819,93252}Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.98,0:01:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96986,98852}I'm leaving Ruka with you, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:98852,101219}Yes, yes. I'll look after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101219,102452}Take it easy, Ruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102452,104086}Dude, we'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:104086,105652}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113586,115886}I thought you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115886,118419}Ruka…\NI will show you no mercy.
