Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:03:02.41,Title 3,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:178419,182419}{\blur0.5\fad(300,0)}Volume 3:\NThe Final Confrontation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182852,185952}Please forgive me,\Nbut I know nothing about etiquette…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185952,188686}You don't have to worry about\Netiquette in this house, Ruka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188686,189686}Thank you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191452,194886}{\i1}Katsuyuki's mother\Ndidn't hear about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195119,197386}{\i1}I was very grateful for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198186,203386}{\i1}I didn't know yet what to say about yesterday,\Nand she never asked me any questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204719,206352}Ruka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206919,208686}Your tea will get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208686,209319}Thank you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211286,213252}Girls are good…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213819,217919}If I had such a lovely daughter,\NI could teach her the art of tea ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218386,220252}Who can it be at this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223686,227619}We are Kobayakawa Ruka's parents.\NWe would like to take our daughter home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227619,229119}Oh, did she do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229419,234286}{\fscx90}We were cautious about our daughter's relationship\Nwith your son, but now she ran away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234286,235552}{\i1}What are they doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235919,239252}If she is there,\Nwe would like to take her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240119,244986}{\i1}What to do? If I run away,\NI will only cause more trouble for Katsuyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244986,247152}{\i1}But if I go back,\NI'll play right into Rumi's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247452,250652}My son did leave Ruka-san\Nunder my care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251152,252152}Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252152,253219}Ruka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253219,256619}I will go with my parents.\NThank you very much for your hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258519,260919}It hurts! Let go of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264419,266052}{\i1}Where's Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266052,268286}{\i1}I thought she'd be\Nwaiting for me outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268819,271752}{\i1}If she's not here, it means\Nshe must be with Katsuyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271752,272719}{\i1}She's at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299519,301552}Ruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301552,303419}You were supposed\Nto stay at my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303852,306419}My parents came to pick me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306419,307352}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307352,309852}But Rumi was nowhere to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310052,312886}She completely disappeared.\NNo one at school has seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312886,314486}Then where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315352,318552}No idea. Let's talk\Nto the rest of the club members.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319019,321486}Katsuyuki, are you sure\Nyou're feeling fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321486,324586}Hell yeah I am.\NYou're not infecting anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324586,326452}Let's go search for Rumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328486,329419}Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330152,332819}Oh? Senpai! Uhm…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332819,334652}It's me, Ruka.\NHave you seen Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334652,337319}I think she went to the storeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337786,341252}She went there\Nwith the high jump boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344886,347286}Hey! Anybody there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347286,348852}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351319,352652}Don't tell me she's…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352652,355186}Probably. This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355186,357119}We've got to let the others know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357119,358119}We'll gather everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359719,361352}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361352,364219}Don't let them leave\Nthe school grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364219,366719}I want Katsuyuki-san alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366719,369519}But you can kill Ruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373752,375952}{\i1}They're missing, as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376186,379786}The only people missing are the three\Nfrom the Kawamura's high jump group, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379786,382152}No, we can't find\Ntwo more freshmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382152,384452}Touma, what is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384752,387619}I'd like to ask you\Nto let everyone go home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387619,391286}Rumi is very sick. We're worried\Nthat she might infect other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391286,392752}Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392752,394652}He's saying the truth, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394652,398719}We think that Kawamura-senpai's group\Nmight have been already infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398719,401386}Is her infection an airborne one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401386,404219}No. It should be okay\Nas long as we don't touch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405286,407586}In that case,\Nwe should be looking for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407586,409252}– Yeah!\N– Let's go look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409252,410452}But, sir…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410452,413219}We'll split into groups. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413219,414219}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414886,419086}When we find her, we'll just get\Neveryone tested at the hospital. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420352,423852}They don't grasp the situation\Nnor the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423852,425119}What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432319,433919}Rumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443019,444486}What is she trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451686,453786}What is she thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460719,461752}Found her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461752,462786}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462786,465986}The boys are looking in the east wing,\Nso the west wing is—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465986,467119}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468419,470586}Sorry I scared you.\NDid you find Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471452,473352}It's you, Ruka-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473352,474552}No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474952,479019}Let's split. Mariko, go with me.\NYou two look on the first floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479019,480019}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480686,483719}What does Rumi-senpai\Nsuffer from exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483719,486252}We're not sure yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486252,488952}But I have to say,\Nyou two really look alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489252,494519}I hadn't looked at what clothes you were wearing,\Nso I thought you were Rumi-senpai just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494519,495619}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495619,496852}I can image.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502986,503752}Did you find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503752,505986}Ruka-senpai?\NWhen did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506319,508452}Where's Mariko?\NShe was with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508919,510319}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510319,512419}Ruka was here with me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513052,515386}But you were in the uniform,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515752,516852}Uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517986,519119}It was Rumi, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519119,521086}That's why she\Npoured water on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521086,522619}So, where are they now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522619,524052}They're in the west wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534586,535586}Mariko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543086,546386}I kissed… with Rumi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546386,547652}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550552,551952}Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551952,554152}Rumi must be still\Nsomewhere nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554152,557286}Wait! Something's\Nwrong with Mariko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558019,561219}Her skin is freezing\Nand she's trembling all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561986,564719}Must be the sickness.\NMaybe we still have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582386,586119}Shit. That bitch wants\Nto keep us trapped in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586119,588086}Ruka, let's search for a safe place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589019,593086}What's going on?\NNo one she has infected has died so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593352,595219}Ruka, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601452,602952}{\i1}Her skin went blue…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603086,605286}{\i1}Marine blue, like deep sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614186,615219}Katsuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615219,618352}Her body is changing\Nfrom the infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620519,622452}It's getting back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624652,626352}The pulse stabilized, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626352,627719}No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632152,634352}And so, our cute Mariko\Njoins my little army.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634552,636052}Rumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639119,642286}Damn! When did\Nshe infect all of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642619,644219}What do you want, Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644419,646586}Ruka, you are going to die\Nfrom an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646586,649186}Something will fall on you\Nduring a casual training.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660886,662219}Stop it, Rumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664886,666052}Katsuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666286,667319}"Katsuyuki"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667319,669052}Hmm? "Katsuyuki", huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669052,671019}When did you two become so close?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671319,675219}I can call Senpai…\NI can call Katsuyuki what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676752,680886}If that's how it is, I'll show you\Nsomething cool before I kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680886,684886}I'll let you see which one of us\NKatsuyuki-san really prefers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684886,686386}Right, Katsuyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686386,687819}Don't do it, Rumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687819,689352}Rumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696486,697886}{\i1}Katsuyuki…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700652,704319}All that's left is to wait for\NKatsuyuki-san to come to his senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704819,706152}{\i1}Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706152,708452}{\i1}What did I ever do to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708952,709952}Katsuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713686,715286}Looks like it's starting to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715986,719286}Put him down.\NHis body temperature will drop soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727486,728919}Come with me, Ruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731719,734652}Spread out.\NBlock all exits from the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736386,737619}You have nowhere to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738086,739752}The reaction takes time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739752,743086}It's only a matter of time\Nbefore Katsuyuki-san converts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753319,755486}Hang in there, Katsuyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758486,761319}Mr. Tajima! Mr. Ougi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761619,764286}What are you doing here\Nat this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764686,767219}{\i1}Thank goodness. They're unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771052,772152}Sir, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772419,772952}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772952,774486}What… What's with you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775486,776586}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776719,778519}Hey, now…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780652,783519}Anybody who tries\Nto defy me… will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:19.58,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:797052,799586}{\fad(200,100)}Biology Room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804652,808219}{\i1}His hand…\NKatsuyuki's hand is so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808219,810086}Katsuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810086,811952}I'm all right… for time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812186,815286}No, Katsuyuki…\NYou shouldn't go anywhere now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815919,818052}Come with me, Ruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823719,824919}What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830119,832052}Katsuyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833252,837519}Ruka, if my pulse stops,\Nuse this to finish me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839786,844219}I'm telling you to kill me\Nbefore I start to convert.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844219,847919}This is the main artery.\NYou can feel the pulse here, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849219,851986}No! I could never\Ndo this, Katsuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851986,854052}Ruka, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854052,857319}If you don't do it,\Nit's likely that I'll try to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857319,861352}Watch my pulse.\NIf it stops, do not hesitate, got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873952,875652}{\i1}Please, keep beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875652,878652}{\i1}If you are going to die,\NI want to die with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880186,881219}Katsuyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881819,883086}Katsuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883086,885586}Get a hold of yourself, Katsuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.21,0:14:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890219,893386}It appears to me that\NKatsuyuki-san's conversion is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893652,895786}Katsuyuki won't convert\Nor whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895786,898352}He will never listen to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900186,901952}Nobody has resisted me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:903019,905419}Katsuyuki-san,\Nstand up and come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906252,907886}Come on, Katsuyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910586,911819}Katsu—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915819,918286}Yes. Walk towards me,\NKatsuyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921486,923219}Stop it! Don't go to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925086,926652}I'm so happy, Katsuyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926852,928119}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928519,932086}Now, I have a small favor to ask.\NCould you kill Ruka for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936119,937486}This is not real.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950019,952252}Ruka, run as fast\Nas you can on my sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956686,957852}Come, Ruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967786,969519}{\i1}I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969519,971652}{\i1}Why is it not working on him alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972452,973986}Are you okay, Ruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973986,975552}Never mind about me,\Nwhat about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975752,978752}Not sure, to be honest.\NOne moment, it stopped and I got calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978752,981552}So she didn't infect you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981752,982652}Looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982652,984352}But why? How is this possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984352,985486}It's thanks to you, Ruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985486,986819}Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986819,990252}Exactly. Remember,\NI kissed with you before Rumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995152,997586}Nothing else comes to my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997586,1001052}Your blood probably carries\Nsome kind of antibodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001052,1003052}Antibodies? In my blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003052,1008519}{\fscx95}You both have the same physique and everything,\Nbut on the day you got infected, Rumi went crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008519,1013119}and you managed to suppress the virus.\NThis was the big difference between you twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013119,1015652}Thus, you developed\Nantibodies, so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015652,1018052}I don't even want to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:16:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018052,1019152}I can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019752,1021886}Another day full of action again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021886,1023986}Let's go back and take some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023986,1026119}I'll talk to my folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026119,1028086}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033386,1035086}{\i1}So frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035086,1037652}{\i1}This is not at all what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037652,1041652}{\i1}I only have control\Nover those I don't care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041652,1043986}{\i1}I don't give a damn\Nwhat happens next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045352,1047386}Ruka! Just you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047386,1049386}Soon it will be full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060352,1061686}Oh? We don't have sweet sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061686,1063419}I will go and buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063419,1064686}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064686,1066186}I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066186,1067386}Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068319,1069652}It's full moon tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069652,1071419}I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071419,1076286}It'll be fine.\NRumi will be stronger, but so will you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:17:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077086,1078286}So will I?…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087586,1089919}Honey, could you please\Nmake me some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089919,1091419}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094786,1097386}Oh? That is strange…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097519,1099119}I am sure I closed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116786,1118519}Whose turn is next?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118519,1120519}Honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134319,1137552}Dad… Dad!\NSomething happened to Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151652,1152652}It's Takashi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152652,1153652}Takashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155786,1157119}M-Mom!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159119,1160319}Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161552,1162986}Takashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166686,1167986}Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167986,1169986}What the fuck is going on, Takashi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169986,1171686}T-That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171686,1173219}Rumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173219,1175852}Rumi-san did this to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175852,1177286}Rumi was here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177286,1179219}Talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182486,1184119}Don't come any closer,\Nyou murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184552,1186052}Takashi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186052,1187952}You monster! You killed them—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187952,1189519}Calm down, Takashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190119,1192119}Ruka, can you go\Nto the next room for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201119,1204686}{\i1}This is just not happening.\NThis is too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213152,1214319}Are you there, Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214319,1218252}Come to the pier tonight at midnight.\NWe have to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221352,1222586}Ruka…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222586,1224019}Are you willing to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224019,1225186}I won't forgive her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226086,1228886}I'll go with you.\NTell me the place and the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228886,1231886}I'll come to you as soon as\Nthe police questioning is over.{NOTE:xxx}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231886,1233786}B-But…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233786,1236586}I won't let something\Nlike that happen ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236586,1240352}We're going to capture her, investigate\Nyour sickness and return her back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240352,1243819}It will be my last gift to my late folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243819,1244752}Katsuyuki…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,0:20:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245752,1247719}You did nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.65,0:21:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266652,1268019}What did you want to discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.25,0:21:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268252,1272952}I've never hated you as much as I did today.\NI won't forgive you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273219,1279186}Even if I'm tied up or locked up somewhere,\NI won't let you do as you please anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.48,0:21:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280486,1282552}Do you seriously think\Nyou can stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282552,1286119}We are identical twins.\NWe got infected with the same virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286486,1289886}I'm the only one who can stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289886,1291886}Don't get cocky, bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1291886,1295752}We have no choice but to fight\Nuntil either of us will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301719,1306286}You just started to use your powers,\Nand you dare to challenge me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309286,1311252}Interesting.\NGive me your best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322552,1325052}{\i1}I don't stand a chance.\NShe's way too powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327552,1328552}Ruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328552,1329952}Katsuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329952,1330819}Ruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.35,0:22:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1341352,1342319}Ruka…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.95,0:23:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1384952,1386052}Ruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.05,0:23:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1386052,1387152}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.15,0:23:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1387152,1388052}Where's Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.08,0:23:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1391086,1392486}You are already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.48,0:23:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1392486,1394152}Snap out of it, Rumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.15,0:23:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1394152,1395019}Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.01,0:23:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1395019,1397286}Rumi! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.28,0:23:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1397286,1400552}My blood is the key\Nto treat your condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.55,0:23:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1400552,1404386}You know what I'm talking about, Rumi!\NMy blood is the reason Katsuyuki stayed normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.75,0:23:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1406752,1407919}She's speaking the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.91,0:23:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1407919,1413619}So, please, let's end all this and\Nget you examined at the hospital once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.61,0:23:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1413619,1415252}And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.75,0:23:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1417752,1422919}{\fscx95}We'll just pretend nothing happened and go back\Nto the days when we both longed for Katsuyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.91,0:23:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1422919,1423919}Rumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.61,0:23:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1424619,1427786}You and I were exactly the same,\Nin every single aspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:23:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1427786,1430386}The appearance. The constitution.\NHow we were raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.58,0:23:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1430586,1435619}Yes. Everything had been the same until that day.\NThe day when Katsuyuki-san confessed to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.68,0:24:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1447686,1451352}The following day,\Nwe were infected with the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.78,0:24:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1460786,1464919}If there was any difference\Nbetween us on that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.91,0:24:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1464919,1467086}it had to do with Katsuyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.51,0:24:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1467519,1471552}For me, it was the happiest day in my life.\NFor you, it was the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.91,0:24:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1471919,1473119}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.11,0:24:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1473119,1476452}Since then our paths have diverged.\NOr do you think I'm wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.45,0:24:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1476452,1478486}No. That's probably the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.95,0:24:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1478952,1483186}I do not regret\Nthat we parted our ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.35,0:24:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1484352,1487186}At first, I was going\Nto congratulate you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.78,0:24:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1487786,1490652}But I realized that it would be\Npure hypocrisy on my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.38,0:24:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1491386,1495086}I don't really want to give\NKatsuyuki-san to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.45,0:25:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1495452,1500919}What I do or whom I kill\Nceased to matter for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.68,0:25:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1501686,1504152}I want Katsuyuki-san for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.15,0:25:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1504152,1506019}Rumi! Rumi, open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.01,0:25:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1506019,1508752}I hate you!\NI can't even look at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.75,0:25:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1508752,1512986}You have the same face, the same voice!\NYou're the only one I cannot ever forgive!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.21,0:25:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1524219,1526619}If you want me that badly, so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.71,0:25:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1528719,1530619}But my heart will never be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.61,0:25:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1530619,1533052}My feelings won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.51,0:25:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1533519,1535886}I'm only giving you my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.88,0:25:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1535886,1538419}Kill me if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.41,0:25:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1538419,1541152}Then do with me as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.15,0:25:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1541152,1542719}But in return,\Nthis ends here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.71,0:25:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1543719,1547186}You will not kill anyone else,\Nand you will stop harassing Ruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.28,0:25:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1548286,1550286}Katsuyuki-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.28,0:25:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1550286,1551419}can be mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.11,0:25:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1552119,1553919}– Rumi, don't!\N– Stay out of this, Ruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.91,0:25:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1553919,1556286}Rumi, what do you think\Nwill happen if you kill Katsuyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.28,0:25:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1556286,1558352}You love him!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.35,0:26:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1558352,1561286}You can't kill him!\NDon't you get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.28,0:26:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1561286,1563386}It's you who doesn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.38,0:26:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1563386,1566052}Katsuyuki-san said\Nhis feelings wouldn't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.18,0:26:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1567186,1572919}So if I don't want anyone to have\NKatsuyuki-san, the only option is to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.95,0:26:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1578952,1581286}Katsuyuki-san will become mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.71,0:26:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1588719,1589852}Don't do it, Rumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.45,0:26:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1594452,1595786}Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.15,0:26:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1598152,1599186}Katsuyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.85,0:26:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1613852,1614652}Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.78,0:27:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1619786,1620552}Rumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.55,0:27:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1620552,1624119}I can't kill him!\NI can't kill Katsuyuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.31,0:27:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1624319,1627819}{\i1}That's right.\NYou would never kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.81,0:27:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1627819,1631352}{\i1}You turned back to normal\Nin the last moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.35,0:27:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1631352,1633486}{\i1}It's better to think that way, Rumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.75,0:27:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1634752,1638686}{\i1}Rumi, even when you get charged\Nwith all these murders,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.68,0:27:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1638686,1641686}{\i1}I will watch over you\Ntill the bitter end.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.88,0:27:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1642886,1646786}{\i1}Because you are\Nmy other self, after all.
Comment: 0,0:27:31.38,0:27:31.38,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1651386,1651386}Ending
